OL,3,CChurch minister tells trial Donaldson
OL,4,Cwanted to 'repent'
OL,6,FA man became emotional as he told a
OL,7,Fcourt of the moment his wife revealed
OL,8,Fto him alleged sexual abuse by former
OL,9,FDUP leader Sir Jeffrey Donaldson when
OL,10,Fshe was a child.
OL,12,FThe witness said his wife was scared
OL,13,Fas she told him about the alleged
OL,14,Fincidents and he realised "this was
OL,15,Fmassive for her".
