OL,3,CChurch minister tells trial Donaldson
OL,4,Cwanted to 'repent'
OL,6,FNewry Crown Court also heard about a
OL,7,Fmessage sent by Jeffrey Donaldson to a
OL,8,Fchurch minister who had been providing
OL,9,Fpastoral support to the couple stating
OL,10,Fhe just wanted to "find a way to say
OL,11,Fhow sorry I am".
OL,13,FEx-MP Donaldson, 63, has pleaded not
OL,14,Fguilty to 18 alleged offences.
OL,16,FThe charges include one count of rape
OL,17,Fand allegations of indecent assault
OL,18,Fand gross indecency, and span a time
OL,19,Fperiod between 1985 and 2008 involving
OL,20,Ftwo alleged victims.
OL,26,@rD@SOUsD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
