FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780665075
OL,3,CChurch minister tells trial Donaldson
OL,4,Cwanted to 'repent'
OL,6,FProsecution barrister Rosemary Walsh
OL,7,FKC asked him about the first time the
OL,8,Fwoman told him about allegations of
OL,9,Fabuse in 2019.
OL,11,FHe became emotional as he told the
OL,12,Fcourt: "She said that when she was
OL,13,Fyounger, Jeffrey had abused her on a
OL,14,Fnumber of occasions."
OL,16,FThe witness said his partner had "gone
OL,17,Finto detail", stating that Donaldson
OL,18,Fhad inappropriately touched her "on a
OL,19,Fnumber of occasions" and that he
OL,20,Fkissed her and "put his tongue down
OL,21,Fher mouth".
