PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780665075
OL,3,CChurch minister tells trial Donaldson
OL,4,Cwanted to 'repent'
OL,6,FHe said she also told him about an
OL,7,Falleged incident where she was "woken
OL,8,Fby a light" and Donaldson was looking
OL,9,Fat her "private parts".
OL,11,FHe told the court that his wife had
OL,12,Frelated another alleged incident to
OL,13,Fhim when "Eleanor had walked in and
OL,14,Fsaw something happen".
OL,16,FHe said: "I was very upset, she was
OL,17,Fslightly surprised by how upset I was.
OL,19,F"She was scared, she had never told
OL,20,Fanyone this, I recognised this was
OL,21,Fmassive for her."
