OL,3,CChurch minister tells trial Donaldson
OL,4,Cwanted to 'repent'
OL,6,FThe witness was cross-examined by
OL,7,FJeffrey Donaldson's barrister Kieran
OL,8,FVaughan and Eleanor Donaldson's
OL,9,Fbarrister, Ian Turkington KC.
OL,11,FLater the court heard evidence from a
OL,12,FPresbyterian minister and his wife who
OL,13,Fhad provided "pastoral support" to
OL,14,FComplainant A and her husband after
OL,15,Fthey had disclosed an allegation of
OL,16,Fabuse.
OL,18,FHe said he had contacted the church's
OL,19,Fhead of safeguarding as he "wanted to
OL,20,Fknow what the boundaries were
OL,21,Fregarding our responsibilities".
OL,26,@uD@NOUuD@_O]{D@\OU}D@_O]
