OL,3,CChurch minister tells trial Donaldson
OL,4,Cwanted to 'repent'
OL,6,FHe said the first meeting took place
OL,7,Fin 2022.
OL,9,FThe witness said when he was on
OL,10,Fholiday in the summer of 2023 he
OL,11,Freceived a message from Jeffrey
OL,12,FDonaldson.
OL,14,FThe court heard that Donaldson asked
OL,15,Ffor the message to be kept "in
OL,16,Fconfidence" and said he did not know
OL,17,F"where else to turn and would truly
OL,18,Fappreciate the opportunity for a
OL,19,Fprivate conversation".
OL,26,@wD@\OUxD@KO]yD@AOU{D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780665075
OL,3,CChurch minister tells trial Donaldson
OL,4,Cwanted to 'repent'
OL,6,FThe minister said he responded the
OL,7,Ffollowing day that it would be
OL,8,F"inappropriate" to have the meeting.
OL,10,FThe court heard that Donaldson then
OL,11,Fsent a reply which said: "I do
OL,12,Funderstand entirely. I don't want to
OL,13,Fcause them further upset.
OL,15,F"I just want to find a way to say how
OL,16,Fsorry I am and repent before them as I
OL,17,Fhave before the Lord."
OL,19,FThe message added: "I will leave it to
OL,20,Fthe Lord and trust that he will find a
OL,21,Fway."
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@OO]sD@ZOUwD@AOUyD@VO]{D@TOU}D@
OL,26,AEO]
