CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780665075
OL,3,CChurch minister tells trial Donaldson
OL,4,Cwanted to 'repent'
OL,6,FThe witness said he did not respond to
OL,7,Fthe message and informed Complainant A
OL,8,Fand her husband.
OL,10,FHe told the court: "I did not want to
OL,11,Fgive any impression I was
OL,12,Fcommunicating outside of this
OL,13,Farrangement behind their back."
OL,15,FThe case will continue on Friday.
OL,17,FJeffrey Donaldson, a former long-
OL,18,Fstanding MP for Lagan Valley, was
OL,19,Farrested and charged at the end of
OL,20,FMarch 2024.
OL,26,@rD@TOUuD@_O]
