OL,3,CChurch minister tells trial Donaldson
OL,4,Cwanted to 'repent'
OL,6,FHe resigned as DUP leader and was
OL,7,Fsuspended from the party after the
OL,8,Fallegations emerged.
OL,10,FWeeks before his arrest, he had led
OL,11,Fthe DUP back into devolved government
OL,12,Fat Stormont after a two-year boycott
OL,13,Fof the powersharing institutions.
